title: Virginia robbery suspect who caused manhunt gets 32 years in prison
text:
Published By: Las Vegas Review-Journal - Today 
A bank robbery suspect who sparked a massive manhunt when he fled a Virginia hospital with a guard's gun was sentenced to 32 years in prison...
